The process logic in BIRT2.2.1 has been changed, so the result is different from BIRT2.0.1.

using "script onRender()" on Cell item instead of highlight can alternate colors
on every row.

you can add the following script:
if ( myCounter % 2 == 0 )
{
	this.getStyle().backgroundColor = "red";
	this.getStyle().color="red";
}

more detail, pls see the attached sample report design.

set WONTFIX.

Thanks.

